{"tid":2424729,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–做運動能增強身體免疫力？","createTime":"2021-02-26T21:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T20:53:40.000Z","uid":38861,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"bc120f732c68a6805bc6a58515f1617e6d277a68","tid":2424729,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T21:21:47.000Z","msg":"骨髓(Bone Marrow)是不少幹細胞的聚居地，而紅血球、白血球、血小板等都是從骨髓裡頭的幹細胞而來。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKvKiJb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKvKiJb.jpg&h=87a240d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖2）老鼠在跑動滾輪運動四星期後，其頭腦骨髓裡專門負責製造免疫細胞的幹細胞數量並沒有明顯改變。<br />\n而在運動時候所用到的腳骨內，專門負責製造免疫細胞的幹細胞數量則有所增加。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8NQegB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8NQegB.jpg&h=b3569b46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）研究發現（Ref1)，骨髓裡某類型的幹細胞表面有著名為Pizeo1的蛋白質。<br />\n當它受到運動等的物理刺激後，便會催動自身幹細胞演變成為骨細胞，同時亦會釋放物質，誘導其他幹細胞演變成為與免疫系統有關的細胞。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zeH429Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzeH429Y.png&h=098689a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n缺乏Pizeo1蛋白質的老鼠當受到細菌感染的時候，所產生的免疫系統細胞數量亦明顯比擁有Pizeo1蛋白質的老鼠為少。<br />\n<br />\n而除運動外，歲數亦會影響與免疫系統有關的幹細胞數量，18個月大的老鼠其數量明顯少於2個月大的老鼠。<br />\n<br />\n若人類亦是採用相同機制的話，這或許是其中一道解釋運動能提升身體免疫力的理據。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2Bx4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=1559e94d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2Bx4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=515da834\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-021-03298-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-021-03298-5&d=FFizHFgeJnC1szROyuQz%2Bx4w7aMtX%2B%2FJ%2BUdoe8qorTI%3D&h=8061b072\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-021-03298-5</a>"},{"pid":"24cc5d6672375a0957003b5a2381b6b6bfd48244","tid":2424729,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T21:39:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4a1d4c76c846d76f0cd1d67889f676946ac1b9","tid":2424729,"uid":105678,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T21:48:24.000Z","msg":"肥婆：跑步傷膝頭！"},{"pid":"7ed9603099119489443c0e354e8652cd0c9eb24e","tid":2424729,"uid":119372,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-26T21:52:55.000Z","msg":"咁係咪仲未有理據證明人類運動能提升身體免疫力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f8211aea4e211acb26052fe7096a9717c060c58","tid":2424729,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T00: